PrecisAppointment of ELWIN HERMANSON of Beechy, Saskatchewan, to be a commissioner of the Canadian Grain Commission to hold office, during good behaviour for a term of five years; and designation of ELWIN HERMANSON to be chief commissioner of the Canadian Grain Commission; effective January 21, 2008.
